                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@bedalton: Why would we compare broofa&apos;s answer to &quot;the e4 version&quot;? The &quot;4&quot; in e4 simply refers to the iteration of optimization and not to the version of UUID, right?&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/114558/rinogo&quot; title=&quot;7,769 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;rinogo&lt;/a&gt;
